\t<div class=\"ly_df_r\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_menuInterview_wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"bl_menuInterview_ttl\">「自分らしく働く」<br>そんな先輩社員たちの1ヶ月</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/ja/recruit/onemonth/01/\">名古屋事業本部　技術統括部<br>設備第一部　第一課　主任<br>牧野 浩大さんの1ヶ月</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/ja/recruit/onemonth/02/\">エンジニアリング本部　<br class=\"sp\">東京設計統括部<br>建築設計部　主任<br>浅野 真未さんの1ヶ月</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"icon_arrow_r pc\"><a href=\"/ja/recruit/interview/\">社員インタビュー</a></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</header>\n\n\t\t<main class=\"ly_main\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"hero\">\n\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/ja/recruit/assets/img/c_info/hero_sp.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/ja/recruit/assets/img/c_info/hero.jpg\" alt=\"中途採用要項 イメージ\">\n\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_h1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>中途採用要項</h1>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"breadcrumb float\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"breadcrumb_list\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://www.ce-kk.co.jp/ja/recruit/BreadcrumbList\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"breadcrumb_item\" itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://www.ce-kk.co.jp/ja/recruit/ListItem\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/ja/recruit/\" itemprop=\"item\"><span itemprop=\"name\">TOP</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"1\" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"breadcrumb_item\">中途採用要項</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<section class=\"bg_white\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_index_ttl\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/ja/recruit/assets/img/recruit/recruit_txt_sp.svg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/ja/recruit/assets/img/recruit/recruit_txt.svg\" alt=\"RECRUIT\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t<section class=\"sec_job-description\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bl_h2\">募集要項</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>施工管理</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>空調・給排水衛生（1級管工事施工管理技士）<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t電気（1級電気工事施工管理技士）<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t建築（1級建築工事施工管理技士）<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tいずれも、<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t名古屋事業本部　／　東京事業本部　／　大阪事業本部<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t各事業本部において若干名</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t<section class=\"sec_benefits\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bl_h2\">勤務・待遇</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>給与支給例</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>年収概算　30～39歳　650～880万円　／<br class=\"sp\">40～60歳　730～1,000万円</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>賞与</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>夏期、冬期の年二回<br>※支給対象期間は前年度実績による</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>勤務時間</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>9:00～17:30（休憩 12:00～13:00）</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>休日休暇</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>週休2日制、祝日、年末年始（12月29日～1月3日）、年次有給休暇（初年度14日～）</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>通勤費</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>全額支給</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t<section class=\"sec_flow\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bl_h2\">応募・選考</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>応募方法</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>電話、又はE-mailにて随時受付</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>選考の流れ</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>エントリー&emsp;<span class=\"pc\">…………………………　</span><br class=\"sp\">&emsp;<span class=\"pc\">&ensp;</span>&nbsp;担当者宛に電話、又はE-mailにて応募連絡</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>書類選考&emsp;<span class=\"pc\">……………………………　</span><br class=\"sp\">&emsp;<span class=\"pc adjustment\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;履歴書・職務経歴書送付</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>第一次面接&emsp;<span class=\"pc\">…………………………　</span><br class=\"sp\">&emsp;&nbsp;人事担当・技術担当面接</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>第二次面接&emsp;<span class=\"pc\">…………………………　</span><br class=\"sp\">&emsp;&nbsp;技術担当役員面接</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>第三次面接&emsp;<span class=\"pc\">…………………………　</span><br class=\"sp\">&emsp;&nbsp;役員面接</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>内定通知</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>本人内定承諾書返送</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t<section class=\"sec_contact\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bl_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bl_h2\">採用窓口・問い合わせ先</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ly_df\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"redline_wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"redline_ttl\">名古屋、関西地区</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>人事部　富岡　<br class=\"sp\"><a href=\"mailto:tomioka.kenji@ce-kk.co.jp\">tomioka.kenji@ce-kk.co.jp</a><br>TEL　052-563-5631<br>〒451-6037<br>名古屋市西区牛島町6番1号<br>名古屋ルーセントタワー37階</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/8FnLruyXY81qEV9Z9\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"bl_btn btn_hover_op\">MAPを見る</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"redline_wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"redline_ttl\">関東地区</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>人事部　三谷　<br class=\"sp\"><a href=\"mailto:mitani.masashi@ce-kk.co.jp\">mitani.masashi@ce-kk.co.jp</a><br>TEL　03-3661-8638<br>〒103-0011<br>東京都中央区日本橋大伝馬町1番4号<br>野村不動産日本橋大伝馬町ビル5階</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"bl_btn btn_hover_op\" href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/1mkhKBK34Wan5LD16\" target=\"_blank\">MAPを見る</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t</main>\n\n\t\t<footer class=\"ly_footer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ly_df\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ly_df_l\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/ja/recruit/\" class=\"footer_logo\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"pc\" src=\"/ja/recruit/assets/img/common/logo_bk.svg\" alt=\"中設エンジ株式会社\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"sp\" src=\"/ja/recruit/assets/img/common/logo_bk_sp.svg\" alt=\"中設エンジ株式会社 CHUSETSU Engineering Co.,Ltd. 名鉄グループ / 伊藤忠グループ\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ly_df_r\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"copyrights\">&copy; 2022 CHUSETSU Engineering Co.,LTD. </span>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</footer>\n\t</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.ce-kk.co.jp/ja/recruit/c_info/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T20:22:01.549Z"}